{"tid":1716381,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［期間限定職業解鎖］病人-邊個無口罩就向邊個咳！","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:28:00.000Z","uid":65292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"97da99103fce1cf5d30b65e0c9831299b03b981a","tid":1716381,"uid":65292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:28:00.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n因為轉季天氣轉涼，多左人冷親感冒唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n而手足都會病，但正如病左都要返工，病都要繼續打仗<br />\n<br />\n今時今日都唔戴口罩既都係得藍屍廢人姐<br />\n<br />\n為左提高市民既衛生意識<br />\n<br />\n等佢地理解戴口罩既重要性<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">病左唔好戴口罩！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>同我對住班藍絲塊面咳同打乞痴！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>仲有十日就區選啦，整病一件得一件！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>最最最重要係，我頭先聽完件廢老屌手足，即除口罩對住佢塊面咳左十分鐘</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好。撚。爽！</span></strong>"}]}